|  |  F-01  |  SSH open to internet (`0.0.0.0/0`)           |  EC2 / Security Group  |  Increases attack surface and brute-force risk     |  High        |  Medium  |  High      |  Restrict SSH to trusted IP or remove SSH and use SSM   |  Open    |  |
+--+--------+-----------------------------------------------+------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------+----------+------------+---------------------------------------------------------+----------+--+
|  |  F-02  |  No SSM role attached to EC2                  |  EC2 / IAM Role        |  Requires reliance on SSH/key-based access         |  Medium      |  Medium  |  Medium    |  Attach EC2 role with `AmazonSSMManagedInstanceCore`    |  Open    |  |
+--+--------+-----------------------------------------------+------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------+----------+------------+---------------------------------------------------------+----------+--+
|  |  F-03  |  IAM user has AdministratorAccess             |  IAM User              |  High blast radius if account is compromised       |  High        |  High    |  Critical  |  Replace with least-privilege policy and MFA            |  Open    |  |
+--+--------+-----------------------------------------------+------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------+----------+------------+---------------------------------------------------------+----------+--+
|  |  F-04  |  CloudTrail not enabled                       |  AWS Account           |  Reduced audit visibility and forensic capability  |  Medium      |  High    |  High      |  Enable multi-region CloudTrail with management events  |  Open    |  |
+--+--------+-----------------------------------------------+------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------+----------+------------+---------------------------------------------------------+----------+--+
|  |  F-05  |  S3 public access settings not fully blocked  |  S3 Bucket             |  Risk of accidental exposure                       |  Medium      |  High    |  High      |  Enable Block Public Access and review bucket policy    |  Open    |  |
